Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.03,0:24:21.67,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,450)}玻璃上的彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.79,0:24:26.68,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這個故事純屬虛構。\N與一切現實中人物，團體和事件無關
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:52.10,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是連死人聽了都要張開眼睛的聲音啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.18,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:08.40,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.92,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  味道不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.10,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.02,0:03:19.58,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,還過得去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:20.96,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.33,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我家鄉的鄉土菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.50,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這個味噌汁的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:29.16,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,和醬油的製作方法是一樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:29.87,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.93,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我將媽媽做的味噌帶了一點過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:37.28,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,還有很多   請多吃點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.61,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,去托列茲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:48.08,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯... 好不容易補給物資的聯絡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:52.79,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我和暮羽去接收
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:58.13,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,彈藥   藥品   日用雜貨都已經見底了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.96,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這下終於可以鬆口氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.40,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪留呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.91,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,去克勞先生的工作室，對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:06.99,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:08.29,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.31,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,下午好好練習號角啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.32,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:51.70,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,飯來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:53.04,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.92,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不像樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:58.11,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你老爸看到你這樣子會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:02.53,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,誰管他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.71,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧  茶點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:18.27,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,占卜仙貝嗎？ {Comment: aren't these fortune cookies？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.79,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一點沒變  還是很討厭這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:24.20,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,教會的孩子們沒做錯什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:31.14,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,以派不上用場的迷信裝飾一下來的騙錢手法，放到哪裡都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.48,0:05:34.51,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦  沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.68,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:41.56,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...   這是...
