Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:30.85,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.60,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,可能晚點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.02,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:40.10,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,別給梨旺前輩添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.19,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.21,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,出發進行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.25,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.42,0:07:00.58,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要求你能做到像我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:04.25,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但用吹嘴練習音高控制是基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.73,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.73,0:07:11.91,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.90,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,基地的生活怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.54,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:26.59,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,說話果斷的地方就是你的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.18,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這股傻氣  我都有點羡慕你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:35.93,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  你為什麼想進軍隊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:37.58,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…  就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:42.61,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說能免費學樂器……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.87,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:49.01,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,保衛國家也是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:53.58,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  錢還是別的什麼原因都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:59.59,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,有明確的目標的人比漫無目的的傢伙更能堅持
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.96,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,唔…	慚愧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:08.92,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，梨旺前輩是為什麼進了軍隊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:11.82,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.50,0:08:16.10,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，剛好和你是相反的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:20.35,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不過想學樂器這點很罕見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:24.98,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是銅管樂器  軍隊以外的人是不會聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:28.31,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前聽到過…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:32.12,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,像前輩一樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.28,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,彼方！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.83,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,天空之音...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.04,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 振作一點  振作點  彼方！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.24,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,回答我！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.29,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.24,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.22,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很熱呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:13.21,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很熱啊…  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.20,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,熱嗎？  是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:18.16,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:29.33,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,媽…  媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.06,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  彼方？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.59,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,彼方！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.35,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,想吃…  雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.01,0:09:44.97,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.16,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,雪呢  雪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.32,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,有才怪了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.72,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,鎮定點   鎮定點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:06.79,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,藥呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:17.30,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,... 不行  那是最後的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:28.54,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,藥呢？ 藥呢？  藥呢？  藥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.69,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,有了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.11,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不少東西都用光了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.95,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,後勤部的混蛋們！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.17,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  怎麼辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:48.63,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡... 該怎麼辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.93,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.54,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,噢...  你好...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.07,0:12:05.97,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,請問有什麼要事麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:09.67,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說，小孩子們又給您添麻煩了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.53,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來的不到之處還請原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.02,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.72,0:12:18.05,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,請幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.49,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:33.82,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.13,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,燒的有點兒厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:45.14,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但喝了藥之後會好一點的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:47.70,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼棘手的病吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:51.56,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是…	三日熱（瘧疾）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.95,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,三日熱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:54.14,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是小孩子得的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:59.72,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是大人  也會因為體力虛耗過度等原因患上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:07.76,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我們教會的孩子們被領養之後  經常有患上這種病的孩子出現
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:12.47,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,平常看上去很健康  一下子就發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.76,0:13:16.49,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,她一直在堅持著呢  一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.49,0:13:21.98,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那…	彼方的病會好轉嗎？ 一直這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:24.52,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我想不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:30.45,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:38.46,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你…	嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.96,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫弓奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:49.49,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這是用藥草煎的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.97,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,再等一段時間煲給她喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.99,0:14:00.12,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那個，麻煩你了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.06,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,請別掛在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.99,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,為這個城市的大家盡力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.53,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的榮幸  也是義務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.62,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  為你們祈禱眾神的寵愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.19,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,感謝你的幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:14.96,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:20.13,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.99,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.38,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:39.15,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我是味噌…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.88,0:16:40.77,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,今天早晨的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:41.96,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:47.53,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,味噌殘渣是製作味噌湯的時候，味噌濾過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.59,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,殘留下來的豆渣就是味噌殘渣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.17,0:16:54.36,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是包袱  是累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:59.28,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,小時候開始一直這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:05.88,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我決定這次一定要加油，不要給大家添麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:07.97,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.83,0:17:14.32,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,表面上看不出來  你心思挺纖細的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:18.10,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,而且  是個任性的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:25.36,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我說了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:27.48,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:38.91,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對了  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:40.97,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.42,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,前輩剛才哼的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.39,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,你…	你在說甚麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.94,0:17:48.54,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:07.03,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人驚訝，只不過聽過一遍…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:08.83,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不止一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:13.15,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前聽過的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:16.69,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,那個曲子  自己也能吹出來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.88,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:25.41,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,吹奏出那天籟之音是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:32.73,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，果然味噌渣到哪裡都是味噌渣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:34.36,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.72,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都依靠教會的話會讓我很生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:43.70,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這個建御雷是舊時代的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:47.83,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的裡面有很多東西沉睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.09,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很多？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:53.25,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  詳細的去問乃繪留吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.74,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,很好  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.28,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:23.82,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…  這個曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:05.97,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這大概就是那個曲子完整的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:12.05,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,好多種樂器，不同的部分交響演奏，組成一曲完整的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.97,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,和駕駛戰車是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:24.82,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,戰車長  炮手  操縱手還有通信手    大家齊心協力  開動一輛戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.68,0:20:27.54,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有不需要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.35,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有不需要的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:40.32,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,別用那種眼神看我　　只不過現學現賣罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:45.06,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是我最憧憬的，最尊敬的一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.94,0:20:53.14,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,借那人的說話來問  彼方  你認為前輩和長官是為什麼而存在的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.25,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓後輩麻煩自己而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:04.66,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行沒關係，好好記住這悔恨感和無力感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:07.51,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,還有那份受照顧的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:14.23,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這會成為你日後照顧別人時寶貴經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.13,0:21:21.73,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,所以  隨時都可以來添我的麻煩    我也是這樣從一路走過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:26.00,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,當然  犯錯的時候我會斥責  也會加以懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:30.26,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  苦惱的時候要說  痛苦的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:32.84,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.01,0:21:40.43,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:44.85,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,以後我會給前輩添很多很多麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:47.05,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:53.83,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,還請手下留情…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:22:01.34,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的   早知道就留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.34,0:22:05.80,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,竟讓梨旺前輩來看護  彼方這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:10.93,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的  只不過是累倒了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.56,0:22:12.80,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,睡一覺就恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:21.04,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,建御雷被人動過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:26.79,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  用了一下    出了甚麼問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:28.02,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:30.64,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,聽了嗎  那個曲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:32.66,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:36.53,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說再也不聽的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.53,0:22:39.33,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,不由得…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.91,0:22:42.63,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.69,0:22:46.08,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.08,0:22:48.08,Sora Chi dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
